Invocation Name: baby girl names
des:
Picking a baby name is hard! Sometimes is just takes hearing the right name to make everything click. 

This skill brings over 1000 baby names and their accompanying origins to you to give you ideas wherever you and Alexa are. Just ask for a girls name and maybe you'll find the one!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
